description:
Bicep module templates used by DEVDEER.

This package is mainly for internal usage at DEVDEER. However most of the conventions are related to the suggestions in the Microsoft Cloud Adoption Framework (CAF).

We also tried to provide much freedom by parametrize our modules a lot.
releaseNotes:
- The webtest component is completely overhauled and far better configurable. It also uses the newest available API. Web tests not have far more options than before.
- The webtest can now be deployed as a standard test.
- Options now return the additionalName if it was passed in.
- All name-builder-occurences now finally use the separator from the naming conventions.
- API-Management resources no longer use the unsupported `2024-05-01` BICEP API version.
- Container Apps deploy with the correct, full custom domain, following the naming conventions.
- Container Apps add their managed identity as environment variable by default.
- Fixed role assignments for container app environment.
- Added types for container apps in ./types/complex.
title: DEVDEER Bicep Modules
